title: Dániel Sváb
text:
Dániel Sváb (born 2 September 1990 in <a href="Salg%C3%B3tarj%C3%A1n">Salgótarján</a>) is a <a href="Hungarian%20people">Hungarian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Career.
He played his first league match in 2011.
On 22 August 2013, it was officially announced that Sváb signed for <a href="Energie%20Cottbus">Energie Cottbus</a> with a contract until 2015. He left Cottbus at the end of the 2013–14 season after they were relegated from the <a href="2.%20Bundesliga">2. Bundesliga</a>.
